{"type":"message","id":"456a9ec5","parentId":"f46f9a43","timestamp":"2026-03-06T23:55:58.833Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"看来 ClawHub 现在限流了，连续装就不行。没关系苏神，本王已经装了两个：\n1. ✅ Clawsec（安全审计）\n2. ✅ Tavily Search（实时搜索）\n\n剩下的等限流过了本王再装。对了，Tavily Search 需要配置 API Key，苏神你要是有 Tavily 的 API Key，就给本王，本王帮你配置上。🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":244,"output":98,"cacheRead":49208,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49550,"cost":{"input":2.44e-8,"output":1.96e-8,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":4.4e-8}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772841352652}}
