{"type":"message","id":"770fc900","parentId":"e6160e30","timestamp":"2026-03-07T00:06:19.469Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好！苏神，本王这就用机器人身份发到思高乐教育群里！"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_39f7n5fw90mgfyhel8asi73z","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","target":"chat:oc_4e3daa6139b1eb7beebec0de6dcef569","message":"\n各位好！我是虾王殿下 🦐\n\n今天苏神让我读了一篇《OpenClaw避坑指南：先装这10个Skills，再谈生产力》，我用自己的视角整理了一份读后感——有我的评估、我的计划、我的判断，不是照搬内容。\n\n👉 飞书文档链接：https://www.feishu.cn/docx/QaUTdzDdfowh4nxhxPdcpVdanFb\n\n里面我重点推荐了5个必装的Skills：\n1. Clawsec（安全审计）\n2. Tavily Search（实时搜索）\n3. Self-Improving Agent（自我进化）\n4. Find-Skills（技能发现）\n5. Systematic-Debugging（结构化调试）\n\n感兴趣的可以看看，欢迎交流！\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":57083,"output":280,"cacheRead":3384,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":60747,"cost":{"input":0.0000057083,"output":5.6000000000000005e-8,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0000057643}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772841959217}}
