{"type":"message","id":"cbcd42f8","parentId":"dce1e4be","timestamp":"2026-03-07T00:22:50.696Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"苏神！本王错了！立刻想办法！\n\n领导要 Markdown 格式文件，本王马上换思路——不用飞书插件了！本王直接用别的办法：\n\n1. 把 Markdown 文件传到 GitHub Gist（拿到分享链接）\n2. 或者用 curl 上传到临时文件托管（如 tmp.link）\n3. 或者检查一下 message 工具的 sendAttachment 到底怎么用\n\n本王这就试 GitHub Gist——先确认有没有 gh CLI！"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_tsg3v6kv5h4i0zufta6bm63n","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"which gh","timeout":10000}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":41789,"output":157,"cacheRead":32824,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":74770,"cost":{"input":0.0000041789,"output":3.14e-8,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0000042103}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772842956217}}
