{"type":"message","id":"3a00bbff","parentId":"2e6591f5","timestamp":"2026-03-07T00:30:03.745Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"苏神！本王记住了！刻骨铭心！🦐\n\n立刻写到今天的 memory 里，以后绝不再犯！"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7jyi7hnfibb3qvxqi71vsp0t","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-07.md","content":"\n# 2026-03-07 虾王日记\n\n## 📌 重要教训（必须记住！）\n\n### 飞书发本地文件的正确方式\n- ❌ 错误：用 `path`、`filePath` 参数\n- ❌ 错误：给飞书文档链接\n- ❌ 错误：给 GitHub raw 链接\n- ✅ 正确：用 `message` 工具的 `sendAttachment`，**参数必须是 `media`，值是本地文件的绝对路径**\n\n示例：\n```python\nmessage(\n    action=\"sendAttachment\",\n    media=\"/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/文件名.md\"\n)\n```\n\n---\n\n## 今天的成果\n1. 装了 Clawsec、Tavily Search、Multi Search Engine、Find-Skills\n2. 用虾王视角写了《OpenClaw避坑指南》读后感\n3. 成功用 `message sendAttachment media=绝对路径` 把 Markdown 文件发给了苏神\n\n---\n\n_本王记住了！以后绝不再绕弯路！🦐_\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":52574,"output":343,"cacheRead":29496,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":82413,"cost":{"input":0.0000052574,"output":6.86e-8,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0000053259999999999995}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772843381665}}
