{"type":"message","id":"8b252504","parentId":"0a3d42cc","timestamp":"2026-03-07T02:10:02.773Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"苏神，刚才的 key 是 **Web 服务 Key**（给后端 API 用的，比如 POI 搜索、路径规划），而 `amap-jsapi-skill` 需要的是 **Web 端（JSAPI）Key**（给前端地图 JS 用的），这两个是不同的 key！\n\n不过没关系！本王先试试用这个 key 能不能跑，如果不行，你再去高德开放平台申请一个 Web 端 JSAPI Key 就行！\n\n本王先把这个 key 加到环境变量里，然后生成一个简单的 POI 搜索与路径规划应用！"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5fe286j5yyi0js6ap62p4q31","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"~/.zshrc","old_string":"export AMAP_WEBSERVICE_KEY=690667cbef3d5fc79d6d623887b249c5","new_string":"export AMAP_WEBSERVICE_KEY=690667cbef3d5fc79d6d623887b249c5\nexport AMAP_JSAPI_KEY=690667cbef3d5fc79d6d623887b249c5"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":78406,"output":307,"cacheRead":29496,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":108209,"cost":{"input":0.0000078406,"output":6.140000000000001e-8,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000007902000000000002}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772849374825}}
