{"type":"message","id":"97e9d15e","parentId":"e096aa65","timestamp":"2026-03-07T02:38:21.730Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"苏神！这个仓库太对本王胃口了！里面全是实用的 baoyu 系列 Skills！🦐\n\n## 对本王有帮助的 Skills（推荐）\n1. **baoyu-cover-image** - 生成文章封面图（咱们 workspace 里已经有这个 Skill 了！）\n2. **baoyu-post-to-wechat** - 发布到微信公众号（咱们 workspace 里也有！）\n3. **baoyu-url-to-markdown** - 把 URL 转成 Markdown（以后读文章更方便！）\n4. **baoyu-markdown-to-html** - Markdown 转 HTML\n5. **baoyu-format-markdown** - 格式化 Markdown\n6. **baoyu-compress-image** - 压缩图片\n7. **baoyu-translate** - 翻译\n8. **baoyu-slide-deck** - 生成幻灯片\n\n## 咱们已经有的\n- ✅ baoyu-cover-image（在 ~/.agents/skills/ 里）\n- ✅ baoyu-post-to-wechat（在 ~/.agents/skills/ 里）\n\n苏神，要不要本王把这里面有用的 Skills 复制到咱们 workspace 里？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":117162,"output":261,"cacheRead":3384,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":120807,"cost":{"input":0.0000117162,"output":5.2200000000000004e-8,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000011768399999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772851069457}}
