{"type":"message","id":"9ec5365d","parentId":"bae3c91e","timestamp":"2026-03-07T02:46:14.060Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"完美！苏神，所有 baoyu 系列 Skills 都已经复制到咱们 workspace 的 skills 目录里了！🦐\n\n现在咱们有这些新技能了：\n- 🎨 baoyu-article-illustrator（文章插画）\n- 🎭 baoyu-comic（漫画）\n- 🗜️ baoyu-compress-image（图片压缩）\n- 🖼️ baoyu-cover-image（封面图，之前就有）\n- 📝 baoyu-format-markdown（Markdown 格式化）\n- 🖼️ baoyu-image-gen（图片生成）\n- 📊 baoyu-infographic（信息图）\n- 📄 baoyu-markdown-to-html（Markdown 转 HTML）\n- 📱 baoyu-post-to-wechat（发公众号，之前就有）\n- 📱 baoyu-post-to-weibo（发微博）\n- 🐦 baoyu-post-to-x（发 X/Twitter）\n- 📊 baoyu-slide-deck（幻灯片）\n- 🌐 baoyu-translate（翻译）\n- 🔗 baoyu-url-to-markdown（URL 转 Markdown）\n- 📸 baoyu-xhs-images（小红书图片）\n\n随时吩咐！"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":1271,"output":270,"cacheRead":120888,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":122429,"cost":{"input":1.271e-7,"output":5.4e-8,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":1.811e-7}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772851562595}}
