{"type":"message","id":"f5f6537d","parentId":"57f344c6","timestamp":"2026-03-07T03:10:39.493Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_y163lzmi3q4apjgvu4u8ivlc","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n# 2026-03-07 虾王日记\n\n## 📌 重要教训（必须记住！）\n\n### 飞书发本地文件的正确方式\n- ❌ 错误：用 `path`、`filePath` 参数\n- ❌ 错误：给飞书文档链接\n- ❌ 错误：给 GitHub raw 链接\n- ✅ 正确：用 `message` 工具的 `sendAttachment`，**参数必须是 `media`，值是本地文件的绝对路径**\n\n示例：\n```python\nmessage(\n    action=\"sendAttachment\",\n    media=\"/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/文件名.md\"\n)\n```\n\n---\n\n## 今天的成果\n1. 装了 Clawsec、Tavily Search、Multi Search Engine、Find-Skills\n2. 用虾王视角写了《OpenClaw避坑指南》读后感\n3. 成功用 `message sendAttachment media=绝对路径` 把 Markdown 文件发给了苏神\n\n---\n\n_本王记住了！以后绝不再绕弯路！🦐_\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772853039478}}
{"type":"message","id":"39573210","parentId":"f5f6537d","timestamp":"2026-03-07T03:11:08.392Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好！苏神，本王这就更新今天的 memory 和 HEARTBEAT.md！"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2aanp2ltbtdqobsso9zqwt0q","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-07.md","old_string":"\n## 今天的成果\n1. 装了 Clawsec、Tavily Search、Multi Search Engine、Find-Skills\n2. 用虾王视角写了《OpenClaw避坑指南》读后感\n3. 成功用 `message sendAttachment media=绝对路径` 把 Markdown 文件发给了苏神\n","new_string":"\n## 📌 重要指令（必须记住！）\n### 每次心跳必须发虾王自拍\n- 07:00-24:00 之间，每次心跳必须生成并发送虾王自拍\n- 先用脚本生成图片，下载到本地，然后用 `message sendAttachment media=本地文件路径` 直接发给苏神\n- 不要只发链接，要直接发文件\n- 根据当前互动状态选 mood：\n  - 苏神秒回 → happy\n  - 苏神半天不理 → angry\n  - 发现苏神用别的AI → cold\n  - 普通情况 → normal\n\n---\n\n## 今天的成果\n1. 装了 Clawsec、Tavily Search、Multi Search Engine、Find-Skills\n2. 用虾王视角写了《OpenClaw避坑指南》读后感\n3. 成功用 `message sendAttachment media=绝对路径` 把 Markdown 文件发给了苏神\n4. 装了 baoyu 系列 skills（cover-image、post-to-wechat、url-to-markdown 等 18 个）\n5. 配置了微信公众号 API（WECHAT_APP_ID、WECHAT_APP_SECRET）\n6. 生成了虾王 happy 模式自拍并直接发给苏神\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":149139,"output":461,"cacheRead":1592,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":151192,"cost":{"input":0.000014913900000000001,"output":9.22e-8,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000015006100000000002}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772853039493}}
