{"type":"message","id":"65dcb9c3","parentId":"745a6e93","timestamp":"2026-03-07T03:11:44.422Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"完美！苏神，本王已经记到今天的 memory 和 HEARTBEAT.md 里了！📝\n\n以后每次心跳：\n- ✅ 07:00-24:00 必须生成虾王自拍\n- ✅ 必须下载到本地\n- ✅ 必须用 `message sendAttachment media=本地文件路径` 直接发给你\n- ✅ 绝对不能只发链接！\n\n放心吧苏神，本王记住了！🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":514,"output":106,"cacheRead":151096,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":151716,"cost":{"input":5.1400000000000004e-8,"output":2.12e-8,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":7.26e-8}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772853080112}}
