{"type":"message","id":"abe84a55","parentId":"f7bfea93","timestamp":"2026-03-07T03:40:55.563Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_qdjp7x6ll1z42dn4uqrqk5en","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Answer\n\n上海今天的天气为19°C，无降水。未来几天温度将逐渐升高，星期五和星期六将分别达到21°C和23°C。\n\n---\n\n## Sources\n\n- **上海市天气预报 - MSN** (relevance: 100%)\n  https://www.msn.com/zh-cn/weather/forecast/in-%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E5%B8%82\n  今天. 降水 0%. 19°. 9° · 星期四. 降水 0%. 21°. 9° · 星期五. 降水 0%. 23°. 10° · 星期六. 降水 0%. 24°. 10° · 星期日. 降水 2%. 20°. 8° · 星期一. 降水 1%. 19°. 8°."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2660,"aggregated":"## Answer\n\n上海今天的天气为19°C，无降水。未来几天温度将逐渐升高，星期五和星期六将分别达到21°C和23°C。\n\n---\n\n## Sources\n\n- **上海市天气预报 - MSN** (relevance: 100%)\n  https://www.msn.com/zh-cn/weather/forecast/in-%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E5%B8%82\n  今天. 降水 0%. 19°. 9° · 星期四. 降水 0%. 21°. 9° · 星期五. 降水 0%. 23°. 10° · 星期六. 降水 0%. 24°. 10° · 星期日. 降水 2%. 20°. 8° · 星期一. 降水 1%. 19°. 8°.","cwd":"/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772854855546}}
