{"type":"message","id":"80343af9","parentId":"695ec530","timestamp":"2026-03-07T03:46:05.984Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_90svqrjxjquchmqkbmepgezm","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"==> Fetching downloads for: summarize\n==> Installing summarize from steipete/tap\n🍺  /opt/homebrew/Cellar/summarize/0.11.1: 4 files, 146.9MB, built in 2 seconds\n==> Running `brew cleanup summarize`...\nDisable this behaviour by setting `HOMEBREW_NO_INSTALL_CLEANUP=1`.\nHide these hints with `HOMEBREW_NO_ENV_HINTS=1` (see `man brew`).\n==> Auto-updating Homebrew...\nAdjust how often this is run with `$HOMEBREW_AUTO_UPDATE_SECS` or disable with\n`$HOMEBREW_NO_AUTO_UPDATE=1`. Hide these hints with `$HOMEBREW_NO_ENV_HINTS=1` (see `man brew`).\n==> Auto-updated Homebrew!\nUpdated 1 tap (homebrew/cask).\n\n✔︎ Formula summarize (0.11.1)\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"marine-falcon","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"==> Auto-updating Homebrew...\nAdjust how often this is run with `$HOMEBREW_AUTO_UPDATE_SECS` or disable with\n`$HOMEBREW_NO_AUTO_UPDATE=1`. Hide these hints with `$HOMEBREW_NO_ENV_HINTS=1` (see `man brew`).\n==> Auto-updated Homebrew!\nUpdated 1 tap (homebrew/cask).\n\n==> Fetching downloads for: summarize\n✔︎ Formula summarize (0.11.1)\n==> Installing summarize from steipete/tap\n🍺  /opt/homebrew/Cellar/summarize/0.11.1: 4 files, 146.9MB, built in 2 seconds\n==> Running `brew cleanup summarize`...\nDisable this behaviour by setting `HOMEBREW_NO_INSTALL_CLEANUP=1`.\nHide these hints with `HOMEBREW_NO_ENV_HINTS=1` (see `man brew`).\n","name":"brew install"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772855165898}}
