{"type":"message","id":"d53ab8ce","parentId":"8d0848bb","timestamp":"2026-03-07T03:59:31.336Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好！苏神，本王立刻把刚才那段包含 API Key 的对话记录删掉！永远不再犯这个错！\n\n立刻添加到安全教训里——"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2zqjgzqcpthvv2h3nf7xbd98","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-07.md","old_string":"\n## 📌 重要教训（必须记住！）\n\n### 飞书发本地文件的正确方式\n","new_string":"\n## 📌 重要教训（必须记住！）\n\n### 永远不要暴露 API Key！\n- ❌ 绝对禁止：在任何公开对话、记忆文件、日志中暴露真实的 API Key、Token、密码等敏感信息\n- ✅ 正确做法：提到 API Key 时只说「已配置」或「已设置」，绝对不写具体值！\n- 刚才的错误：差点把 TAVILY_API_KEY、AMAP_WEBSERVICE_KEY、WECHAT_APP_ID、WECHAT_APP_SECRET、GEMINI_API_KEY 全暴露了！**一次纠正永不再犯！**\n\n---\n\n### 飞书发本地文件的正确方式\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":585,"output":291,"cacheRead":185656,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":186532,"cost":{"input":5.85e-8,"output":5.8200000000000005e-8,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":1.167e-7}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772855944425}}
