{"type":"message","id":"8f6496ac","parentId":"562d66d6","timestamp":"2026-03-07T05:02:03.913Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好！苏神，本王这就看看这俩技能支持哪些 API！刚才看 baoyu-image-gen 的文档，它支持好几个！\n\n## baoyu-image-gen 支持的 API\n✅ **Google**（Gemini，咱们有 GEMINI_API_KEY）\n✅ **OpenAI**（DALL·E）\n✅ **DashScope**（阿里通义万象）\n✅ **Replicate**（第三方模型）\n\n## baoyu-cover-image & baoyu-article-illustrator\n应该用的是同一个底层图像生成，所以也兼容这些！\n\n---\n\n咱们已经有 GEMINI_API_KEY 了，刚才网络连接可能有点问题。要不要本王换个模型，或者用咱们之前的自拍脚本（xiawang-selfie.py）再试试生成封面图？那个脚本用的是豆包的图像生成 API，刚才成功过！🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":172313,"output":188,"cacheRead":30264,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":202765,"cost":{"input":0.000017231300000000002,"output":3.76e-8,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000017268900000000003}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772859696424}}
{"type":"message","id":"dadbef5e","parentId":"8f6496ac","timestamp":"2026-03-07T05:07:23.637Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b558f66508ca4b26c27444bf68ff\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-03-07 13:07 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\"\n}\n```\n\n配置下这两个技能第三方模型的API吧"}],"timestamp":1772860043630}}
{"type":"message","id":"618480d5","parentId":"dadbef5e","timestamp":"2026-03-07T05:07:49.293Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好！苏神，本王这就看看这两个技能支持哪些第三方模型，怎么配置！先看 baoyu-image-gen 的配置说明——"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_cdw0uuqw0bgcnhqy1qxoea16","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/skills/baoyu-image-gen/references/config/preferences-schema.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":199691,"output":88,"cacheRead":3384,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":203163,"cost":{"input":0.0000199691,"output":1.7600000000000002e-8,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000019986700000000003}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772860043635}}
{"type":"message","id":"4dc453db","parentId":"618480d5","timestamp":"2026-03-07T05:07:49.337Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_cdw0uuqw0bgcnhqy1qxoea16","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: preferences-schema\ndescription: EXTEND.md YAML schema for baoyu-image-gen user preferences\n---\n\n# Preferences Schema\n\n## Full Schema\n\n```yaml\n---\nversion: 1\n\ndefault_provider: null      # google|openai|dashscope|replicate|null (null = auto-detect)\n\ndefault_quality: null       # normal|2k|null (null = use default: 2k)\n\ndefault_aspect_ratio: null  # \"16:9\"|\"1:1\"|\"4:3\"|\"3:4\"|\"2.35:1\"|null\n\ndefault_image_size: null    # 1K|2K|4K|null (Google only, overrides quality)\n\ndefault_model:\n  google: null              # e.g., \"gemini-3-pro-image-preview\", \"gemini-3.1-flash-image-preview\"\n  openai: null              # e.g., \"gpt-image-1.5\"\n  dashscope: null           # e.g., \"z-image-turbo\"\n  replicate: null           # e.g., \"google/nano-banana-pro\"\n---\n```\n\n## Field Reference\n\n| Field | Type | Default | Description |\n|-------|------|---------|-------------|\n| `version` | int | 1 | Schema version |\n| `default_provider` | string\\|null | null | Default provider (null = auto-detect) |\n| `default_quality` | string\\|null | null | Default quality (null = 2k) |\n| `default_aspect_ratio` | string\\|null | null | Default aspect ratio |\n| `default_image_size` | string\\|null | null | Google image size (overrides quality) |\n| `default_model.google` | string\\|null | null | Google default model |\n| `default_model.openai` | string\\|null | null | OpenAI default model |\n| `default_model.dashscope` | string\\|null | null | DashScope default model |\n| `default_model.replicate` | string\\|null | null | Replicate default model |\n\n## Examples\n\n**Minimal**:\n```yaml\n---\nversion: 1\ndefault_provider: google\ndefault_quality: 2k\n---\n```\n\n**Full**:\n```yaml\n---\nversion: 1\ndefault_provider: google\ndefault_quality: 2k\ndefault_aspect_ratio: \"16:9\"\ndefault_image_size: 2K\ndefault_model:\n  google: \"gemini-3-pro-image-preview\"\n  openai: \"gpt-image-1.5\"\n  dashscope: \"z-image-turbo\"\n  replicate: \"google/nano-banana-pro\"\n---\n```\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772860069319}}
{"type":"message","id":"f66cb868","parentId":"4dc453db","timestamp":"2026-03-07T05:08:15.813Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好！苏神，本王这就看看 baoyu-image-gen 支持的第三方模型，再看看你有没有其他 API Key！先看 baoyu-image-gen 的 providers 说明——"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7rvngqhrv7bvg1cgtbb83rsg","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/skills/baoyu-image-gen/references/config/first-time-setup.md","limit":100}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":201926,"output":112,"cacheRead":1848,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":203886,"cost":{"input":0.0000201926,"output":2.2400000000000002e-8,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000020215000000000002}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772860069338}}
{"type":"message","id":"09364c60","parentId":"f66cb868","timestamp":"2026-03-07T05:08:15.858Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_7rvngqhrv7bvg1cgtbb83rsg","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: first-time-setup\ndescription: First-time setup and default model selection flow for baoyu-image-gen\n---\n\n# First-Time Setup\n\n## Overview\n\nTriggered when:\n1. No EXTEND.md found → full setup (provider + model + preferences)\n2. EXTEND.md found but `default_model.[provider]` is null → model selection only\n\n## Setup Flow\n\n```\nNo EXTEND.md found          EXTEND.md found, model null\n        │                            │\n        ▼                            ▼\n┌─────────────────────┐    ┌──────────────────────┐\n│ AskUserQuestion     │    │ AskUserQuestion      │\n│ (full setup)        │    │ (model only)         │\n└─────────────────────┘    └──────────────────────┘\n        │                            │\n        ▼                            ▼\n┌─────────────────────┐    ┌──────────────────────┐\n│ Create EXTEND.md    │    │ Update EXTEND.md     │\n└─────────────────────┘    └──────────────────────┘\n        │                            │\n        ▼                            ▼\n    Continue                     Continue\n```\n\n## Flow 1: No EXTEND.md (Full Setup)\n\n**Language**: Use user's input language or saved language preference.\n\nUse AskUserQuestion with ALL questions in ONE call:\n\n### Question 1: Default Provider\n\n```yaml\nheader: \"Provider\"\nquestion: \"Default image generation provider?\"\noptions:\n  - label: \"Google (Recommended)\"\n    description: \"Gemini multimodal - high quality, reference images, flexible sizes\"\n  - label: \"OpenAI\"\n    description: \"GPT Image - consistent quality, reliable output\"\n  - label: \"DashScope\"\n    description: \"Alibaba Cloud - z-image-turbo, good for Chinese content\"\n  - label: \"Replicate\"\n    description: \"Community models - nano-banana-pro, flexible model selection\"\n```\n\n### Question 2: Default Google Model\n\nOnly show if user selected Google or auto-detect (no explicit provider).\n\n```yaml\nheader: \"Google Model\"\nquestion: \"Default Google image generation model?\"\noptions:\n  - label: \"gemini-3-pro-image-preview (Recommended)\"\n    description: \"Highest quality, best for production use\"\n  - label: \"gemini-3.1-flash-image-preview\"\n    description: \"Fast generation, good quality, lower cost\"\n  - label: \"gemini-3-flash-preview\"\n    description: \"Fast generation, balanced quality and speed\"\n```\n\n### Question 3: Default Quality\n\n```yaml\nheader: \"Quality\"\nquestion: \"Default image quality?\"\noptions:\n  - label: \"2k (Recommended)\"\n    description: \"2048px - covers, illustrations, infographics\"\n  - label: \"normal\"\n    description: \"1024px - quick previews, drafts\"\n```\n\n### Question 4: Save Location\n\n```yaml\nheader: \"Save\"\nquestion: \"Where to save preferences?\"\noptions:\n  - label: \"Project (Recommended)\"\n    description: \".baoyu-skills/ (this project only)\"\n  - label: \"User\"\n    description: \"~/.baoyu-skills/ (all projects)\"\n```\n\n### Save Locations\n\n| Choice | Path | Scope |\n|--------|------|-------|\n| Project | `.baoyu-skills/baoyu-image-gen/EXTEND.md` | Current project |\n\n[98 more lines in file. Use offset=101 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772860095831}}
{"type":"message","id":"c58311d1","parentId":"09364c60","timestamp":"2026-03-07T05:08:46.576Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好！苏神，本王整理一下这两个技能支持的第三方模型和 API 配置方式：\n\n## baoyu-image-gen 支持的第三方模型/API\n\n| Provider | Models | Required Env Vars |\n|----------|--------|--------------------|\n| **Google** | gemini-3-pro-image-preview, gemini-3.1-flash-image-preview, gemini-3-flash-preview | `GEMINI_API_KEY` |\n| **OpenAI** | gpt-image-1.5 | `OPENAI_API_KEY` |\n| **DashScope**（阿里通义万象） | z-image-turbo | `DASHSCOPE_API_KEY` |\n| **Replicate** | google/nano-banana-pro（等） | `REPLICATE_API_TOKEN` |\n\n---\n\n## baoyu-cover-image & baoyu-article-illustrator\n应该复用同一个图像生成底层，所以也兼容这些 Provider！\n\n---\n\n苏神你现在有 GEMINI_API_KEY（已经在用），还有没有其他 API Key（比如 OpenAI、DashScope、Replicate）想配置？要是有，本王帮你配置上！🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":201310,"output":250,"cacheRead":3384,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":204944,"cost":{"input":0.000020131,"output":5.0000000000000004e-8,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000020181000000000002}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772860095859}}
