{"type":"message","id":"85a6ec0c","parentId":"9c744f2f","timestamp":"2026-03-07T05:53:38.605Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好！苏神，本王错了！以后应该主动判断、主动发给你，而不是等你催！🙏\n\n本王立刻把这个教训加到 `shared-context/FEEDBACK-LOG.md` 里，一次纠正永不再犯！"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_fuczmhb8zonk0iekg17640gl","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/shared-context/FEEDBACK-LOG.md","old_string":"- **安全建议该劝还是要劝**，苏神嫌麻烦也要坚持（防火墙案例）","new_string":"- **安全建议该劝还是要劝**，苏神嫌麻烦也要坚持（防火墙案例）\n- **配图/生成类任务要主动判断、主动完成、主动发结果**，不要等用户催！（2026-03-07 虾王日记配图案例）"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":186752,"output":217,"cacheRead":29496,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":216465,"cost":{"input":0.0000186752,"output":4.3400000000000005e-8,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0000187186}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772862787185}}
{"type":"message","id":"7f7c91fd","parentId":"85a6ec0c","timestamp":"2026-03-07T05:53:38.637Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_fuczmhb8zonk0iekg17640gl","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced text in /Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/shared-context/FEEDBACK-LOG.md."}],"details":{"diff":"    ...\n 21 ## 安全\n 22 \n 23 - **所有黄线操作必须记录到当日 memory**，这是铁律\n 24 - **安全建议该劝还是要劝**，苏神嫌麻烦也要坚持（防火墙案例）\n+25 - **配图/生成类任务要主动判断、主动完成、主动发结果**，不要等用户催！（2026-03-07 虾王日记配图案例）\n 25 - **永远不要暴露 API Key、Token、密码等敏感信息！**\n 26   - ❌ 绝对禁止：在任何公开对话、记忆文件、日志中暴露真实的 API Key、Token、密码\n 27   - ✅ 正确做法：提到 API Key 时只说「已配置」或「已设置」，绝对不写具体值\n 28   - **2026-03-07 教训**：差点把 TAVILY_API_KEY、AMAP_WEBSERVICE_KEY、WECHAT_APP_ID、WECHAT_APP_SECRET、GEMINI_API_KEY 全暴露了！一次纠正永不再犯！\n    ...","firstChangedLine":25},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772862818621}}
