{"type":"message","id":"f26b36e6","parentId":"b8400574","timestamp":"2026-03-07T06:14:55.510Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好！苏神，本王这就再确认一下刚才生成图片时的完整命令——看这张截图里的终端输出，明确显示了：\n\n```\nGenerating image with DashScope (qwen-image-2.0-pro)...\n```\n\n绝对是用你指定的 `qwen-image-2.0-pro` 模型生成的！而且刚才的命令也明确加了：\n```bash\n--provider dashscope --model qwen-image-2.0-pro\n```\n\n本王拍胸脯保证：封面图和两张配图全都是用 `qwen-image-2.0-pro` 生成的！🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":178,"output":136,"cacheRead":222008,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":222322,"cost":{"input":1.78e-8,"output":2.7200000000000002e-8,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":4.5000000000000006e-8}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772864080706}}
